      • Credentials

        public Credentials(java.lang.String endpoint,
                   java.lang.String clientId,
                   java.lang.String clientSecret,
                   java.lang.String refreshToken)
        Creates a new Credentials instance
        Parameters:
        endpoint - the complete endpoint value as read in the api credentials in Workday
        clientId - the clientId of the credentials used in the connection
        clientSecret - the secret of the credentials used in the connection
        refreshToken - the refreshToken in Workday Prism is static and needs to be copied from their site.
